        {
            "title": "鄭裕玲有向吳君如傳訊息問候 獲封「Turbo玲」自認行得太快 恨請男神肖戰做網上節目訪問",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"鄭裕玲有向吳君如傳訊息問候 獲封「Turbo玲」自認行得太快 想請男神肖戰做網上節目訪問\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/d0a96d86a3088641016c54ca82865daf/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250320/_2025032015011835169.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">鄭裕玲有向吳君如傳訊息問候 獲封「Turbo玲」自認行得太快 想請男神肖戰做網上節目訪問</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>鄭裕玲（Do姐）今日（20日）出席家具展覽，對生活有要求的Do姐表示舒適的家居令她拋開煩惱，家具當中對床比較注重，因她愛在床上一邊煲劇一邊歎茶。Do姐亦很會斷捨離，表示不會留戀舊物，沒甚麼不捨得掉，執拾感覺很治癒，衣物會送給朋友。\n\n</p><h2>讚君如孝順</h2>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Do姐出席家具展覽。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/953a52c4bed2d449a1d521ffb10ebc26/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-20_at_2_43_52_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Do姐出席家具展覽。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"對生活有要求的Do姐表示，家具當中對床比較注重。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/efd0c306a25f5deb29435945fbed056e/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-20_at_2_43_52_PM_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        對生活有要求的Do姐表示，家具當中對床比較注重。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Do姐近日與電台節目《口水多過浪花》主持余迪偉、余德丞等去杭州旅行。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/62597471fb7ebe35c38558ac57c36d1b/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-20_at_2_43_52_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Do姐近日與電台節目《口水多過浪花》主持余迪偉、余德丞等去杭州旅行。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"她獲封「Turbo玲」的稱號。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f615f558d2b27b312a6d3581451fcbf4/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-20_at_2_43_53_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        她獲封「Turbo玲」的稱號。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Do姐自認行得太快，行得最慢是余德丞。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b414fa163a12f34bd51fa9e3a0d571c0/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-20_at_2_43_53_PM_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Do姐自認行得太快，行得最慢是余德丞。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"對於吳君如爸爸冬叔離世，Do姐表示有傳訊息問候。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3c7f2098309f813fc82c19507502ae5e/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-20_at_2_43_53_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        對於吳君如爸爸冬叔離世，Do姐表示有傳訊息問候。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Do姐更大讚君如很孝順，但現時不想打擾對方了。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5903e5cdee439bd2b4c9180de87f9899/2025-03/QA7W6187.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Do姐更大讚君如很孝順，但現時不想打擾對方了。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<p>談到近日與電台節目《口水多過浪花》主持余迪偉、余德丞等去杭州旅行，她表示去年去了上海，相隔1年再旅行，本想去家鄉四川重慶，但時間配合不到，今次杭州遊覽西湖，逛街吃喝。談到余迪偉指她在此行多了「Turbo玲」稱號，Do姐自認行得太快，行得最慢卻是余德丞。Do姐亦在杭州與喜歡的肖戰海報合照，她表示希望日後有機會請肖戰接受其網上節目訪問，笑言不需要合作，單是訪問已很開心。另外，談到吳君如爸爸冬叔離世，Do姐表示有傳訊息問候，指君如很孝順，現時不打擾對方了。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2059249/即時-娛樂-鄭裕玲有向吳君如傳訊息問候-獲封-Turbo玲-自認行得太快-恨請男神肖戰做網上節目訪問",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-20 15:21:46",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
