            "title": "南韓戒嚴風波｜總理韓悳洙彈劾案下周一宣判",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"南韓總理韓悳洙。  美聯社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/481a2b3656ae82c59bac69513263c069/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250320/_2025032015140119872.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">南韓總理韓悳洙。  美聯社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>據韓聯社報道，南韓憲法法院周四表示，將於下周一上午10時，宣布總理韓悳洙彈劾案的裁決。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2059252/即時-國際-南韓戒嚴風波-總理韓悳洙彈劾案下周一宣判",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-20 15:21:46",
